Init submodules
----------------
git submodule init
git submodule update

To compile Command-T: rake make (in command-t directory. Install ruby, ruby-dev before)

--KEYS-----------------
<leader>d = NerdTree
<leader>t = Command-T

Search in files
-----------------
:grep pattern filepattern
afterwards use :cw to open quickfix window. 
Still searching for a better way
